
### 7. `.gitignore`

This file specifies which files and directories Git should ignore. Here's a basic setup:

```gitignore
# Node modules
node_modules/

# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# Dependency directories
jspm_packages/

# Optional npm cache directory
.npm

# Optional REPL history
.node_repl_history

# Mac system files
.DS_Store

# Windows system files
Thumbs.db
